<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
right now, im at the barb camp in WK. i actually bind near my camp too, but you have to look at two very important issues when binding near/at your camp.<P>1. Location. <B>dont</B> bind where the mob spawns. be sure to get a safe distance away, where nothing will train on to you. <P>2. Kiting/killing. <B>dont</B> bind where/around where you will be kiting. this may seem obvious, but some people make mistakes/get excited that they have a good spot and just bind where they stand. (oh, and never bind where your medding either, cuz if something sneaks up behind you and aggros while your medding, and you repop in the same spot, get that reset button ready.)<P>Malton McPorter <B>*Tupp*</B><BR>30 halfling druid<BR>bristlebane<P>Inina Anini <B>*Heretics*</B><BR>30 erudite necromancer<BR>torvonnilous (and rebuilding on bristlebane)
