Back to the issue of binding: in FM near the OT zone there is a high flat area on your right as you enter the zone-in tunnel. It's far enough away from any FM spawn spots to avoid having any wanderers intrude on you and high enough to escape having anything trained on you (unless you are *really* unlucky). I bound there for - hm - four levels? with no problems at all.
